<p>
💰 活动价：¥178&nbsp;<strike>（原价&nbsp;<span style="font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">¥198</span>）</strike>
